    "The first principal components of the identified gene/miRNA co-expression modules were then extracted and input into a CoxPH Regression Network 11.",
    "In their study, Huang et al.",
    "observed improved performance of SALMON when more omics data were incorporated.",
    "Cheerla et al.",
    "built a DL model that integrates multimodal representations from clinical, omics, and whole slide image data and performs pan-cancer prognosis prediction 10."
